docs {
  ## Get Episode List by Series (Flat View)

  Returns all episodes across all seasons for a series.
  Uses `seriesId` instead of `seasonId` for a flat view.

  **Prerequisites:** Set `sampleSeriesId` in your environment.

  **Acceptance Criteria:**
  - ✅ Returns all episodes across seasons
  - ✅ Same SegmentInfo shape as season-based query
  - ✅ Requires admin authentication
}
